<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>广西贵港</span></strong><span>市民在买月饼时发现</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>竟有月饼生产日期标注为9月10日</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span>网友戏称</span><strong><span>“早产”月饼</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong></span></p>
<p><strong><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200908/54f78fe757c24dc78468d9d659fe0567.png" /></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">↓↓↓</span></p>
